Subject: Re: [PATCH 1/3 v4] ftrace: Have the callbacks receive a struct
 ftrace_regs instead of pt_regs
Message-Id: <20201107132927.0ae1e567da8559f041dc2227@kernel.org>
In-Reply-To: <20201106214403.138244432@goodmis.org>
